.Dd December 27, 2015
.Dt OPNSENSE-SIGN 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm opnsense-sign
.Nd OPNsense signature generation
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl p Ar prefix Ar file
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility signs arbitrary files by creatig a
.Sq .sig
file, which can then be verified using
.Xr opnsense-verify 8 .
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width ".Fl p Ar prefix" -offset indent
.It Fl p Ar prefix
The prefix to the
.Sq .key
and
.Sq .pub
files to be used for signing.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr opnsense-verify 8
